      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nAuthorization approvals, declines, and reversals from FIS STDAUTH XTRACT v2.7. **Click any tile** to jump to the detail table.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Response Code | `fact_authorization.response_code` | 0=Approved \u00b7 51=Insufficient Funds \u00b7 57=Not Permitted \u00b7 61=Exceeds Limit |\n| Auth Amount | `fact_authorization.authorization_amount` | Requested purchase amount |\n| Purse Name | `fact_authorization.purse_name` | OTC2100 \u00b7 FOD2100 \u00b7 CMB2100 |\n| Is Reversed | `fact_authorization.is_reversed` | True if subsequently reversed |\n| Merchant | `fact_authorization.merchant_name` | Store where card was used |\n| MCC | `fact_authorization.mcc` | Merchant Category Code |\n\n> **395 authorizations** \u2014 364 approved / 31 declined, $16,715 total authorized.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
